pan class=title>   sigh!!!!</span><hr size=1> You know when I earn this weapon I'm not gonna turn to the people who helped me kill the queen of chardok, and helped me kill severilous, and took me to sky, and hate and fear.  I'm not gonna look at the 36 or 42 people who just helped me kill talendor and say.. thank you for supporting me so I can go claim my worthless piece of crap weapon.  I know ONE warrior on my server can outdamage me though so thank you again for helping me achieve suckiness.  <br>
<br>
Don't tell me about how bad it taunts.  Every damn warrior I see now is using 2 hand blunt anyways regardless of it's terrible taunting ability.  So I don't think we are worried about taunt really.<br>
<br>
Don't tell me those stats suck.. because they are freaking incredible..and free as well due to them replacing weapons which, for the most part, have few stat increases.<br>
<br>
If you won't replace you current combo of weapons for these then you have a serious problem.  Damn I remember people screaming at others for not using the 9/25 amy whip over the 8/24 yak back in the day.  This is a huge upgrade.  And to be honest.... it's not like you are gonna skip out on the raids we have to do anyhow.<br>
<br>
I like these blades.  If you won't appreciate these after the few hundred people total help you out to get them.  Then maybe you just don't deserve them.<br>
<br>
Sindarre Frostpaw <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bbrellserilis.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=dantes>Dantes</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://forums.eqrealms.com/ubb/icons/icon10.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Splinterboy</span><br>  Posts: 304<br> <font color=#CC9900>(10/27/00 10:56:03 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.valorblade.com/dantes.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: sigh!!!!</span><hr size=1> Um, the think the point is that a lot of warriors who were originally going to try to get them probably won't even bother asking those few hundred people for help.  So it's not like they don't appreciate them, they just won't ask. <p><img src="http://www.eqrealms.com/dantes_sig.jpg" width="260" height="137"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uthoricofbrell.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Thoric of Brell</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Uber Gimp</span><br>  Posts: 319<br> <font color=#CC9900>(10/27/00 11:27:11 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.facelink.com/edit/raw/rawimage/00/1192400.jpg?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60 WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: sigh!!!!</span><hr size=1> Don't recall ever saying I wouldnt wield them if I got them? Or that I thought they sucked in general. I don't see a problem with people saying &quot;Hey, our quest was a lot harder than 75% of the other quests, and our weapon is not as well thought out or useful as some of the others.&quot; I mean here's the thing... If I have them for a while and then I get a botbde and bf, and discover that they taunt better and do more damage, and stop using the epic weapon because it doesnt work as well, then those hundreds of people who helped us did so for very little. Seems to me when we ask Verant to review this weapon, we do so precisely to validate the effort so many put into achieving it. <br>
<br>
